4Geeks Academy offers a Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence designed for professionals seeking to integrate AI into their roles. Over a span of six weeks, participants will explore various aspects of AI, including generative AI, context, and prompts to enhance workplace productivity. The course features two live online classes each week with a small class size of up to 12 students. An official completion certificate is provided at the end of the course. No prior experience is necessary to enroll. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop